        {
            "title": "川普關稅追蹤：落地概率不足三成 最引人注目的狠話常被收回",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg Economics\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"589\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VrBC1PTEEbr8WDhd8ONd3A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4OQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/4880785a1ccb77b3bbfb934f83250b0f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg Economics</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 在不到三周的時間裡，川普接連發出四項關稅威脅。一般情況下，這類威脅會令投資者感到不安、使企業執行長們神經緊張，經濟學家們會紛紛調低對目標國家的成長預測。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而，金融市場和企業高管們對川普最新涉及伊朗貿易夥伴、格陵蘭島支持者、加拿大和韓國的警告大多表現得不以為意，認為這些僅僅是其為了獲得籌碼或改變對方行為的言論而採取的行動，並不會動真格。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據彭博經濟研究的一項新分析，川普並不總是「認慫」。更準確地說，研究發現他將威脅付諸行動的情況約占四分之一。約43%的威脅後來被撤回（有時伴隨著川普宣稱取得了所謂的勝利），或者從未正式實施。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9c2087b1-2fb1-3b1f-a578-382404bdc116-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：川普威脅提高韓國商品關稅 韓方回應稱將通報對美投資立法進展</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博經濟研究的Nicole Gorton-Caratelli和Chris Kennedy審查了從2024年11月大選到上周日期間，川普發出的 49項關稅威脅或其政府發起的貿易調查（該統計不包括他最新目標韓國）。彭博經濟研究發現，其中超過一半的威脅尚未完全落地。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"499\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vbOrhDU_dF__dL6qUvxOyQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ5OQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/64973836481823bdec7a0b74c1d60e16\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">觀察這49項聲明的時間線可以發現，大多數完全執行或進入調查階段的動作發生在2月至9月之間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">每月的分類數據顯示，隨著對生活成本（負擔能力）的擔憂壓低了他的民意支持率，川普的關稅威脅在去年年底趨於減少。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"589\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zcNAmebYpR.2LHHZNkG5qQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4OQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/1c5ad9ff1dcbfc1163820f5f90dbd1ae\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「這一規律並非絕對完美，」 Gorton-Caratelli和Kennedy在研究報告中寫道。「總的來說，我們看到川普收回了他最引人注目的威脅，而這些威脅往往是那些會劇烈推高美國有效關稅稅率，或威脅到美中貿易休戰的言論。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：歷經近二十年談判 歐盟與印度達成自貿協定</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題TACO Tracking: Trump Carries Out One in Four Tariff Threats (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E8%BF%BD%E8%B9%A4-%E8%90%BD%E5%9C%B0%E6%A6%82%E7%8E%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E4%B8%89%E6%88%90-%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E6%B3%A8%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%8B%A0%E8%A9%B1%E5%B8%B8%E8%A2%AB%E6%94%B6%E5%9B%9E-163127580.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 01:13:08",
