        {
            "title": "美元跌至四年低點 多重不利因素疊加",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 彭博美元指數跌至近四年來的最低水平，日圓再現強勢令美元進一步承壓。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博美元指數一度下跌0.4%，創2022年3月以來最低。這是該指數連續第四個交易日下跌，此前美元單周表現創5月份以來最差。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元下跌源於有跡象顯示，美國可能出手支撐日圓，重新引發關於主要經濟體是否可能協調干預匯市、引導美元兌關鍵貿易夥伴貨幣走低的討論。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nyGi.zx0EtxxIuTfJSgWsw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a5524b299ec7c33bff0c379657f51128\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元疲軟還反映出投資者的謹慎情緒，此前華盛頓的一系列政策反覆無常，其中包括美國總統唐納德·川普威脅接管格陵蘭。從更長期看，圍繞聯儲會獨立性的風險、不斷擴大的預算赤字、對財政放縱的擔憂以及政治極化日益加劇，都在拖累美元下行。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-65dd985f-cca9-3c45-bdf8-ff203ec84ef8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「鑒於政府部分停擺的可能性，看多美元的人仍有不少擔憂，」法國興業銀行外匯策略主管Kit Juckes表示，「美國經濟成長的表現仍可能決定聯儲會的寬鬆幅度，從而決定美元是否會從當前水平明顯走弱。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美元下行壓力積聚 交易員權衡美國協助日本干預匯市的可能性</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Dollar Sinks to Lowest Level in Four Years as Headwinds Multiply</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Carter Johnson、Greg Ritchie.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E8%B7%8C%E8%87%B3%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%B4%E4%BD%8E%E9%BB%9E-%E5%A4%9A%E9%87%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%A9%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E7%96%8A%E5%8A%A0-133812478.html",
