            "title": "滙豐縮減新加坡零售網點 重心繼續向財富管理傾斜",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"滙豐縮減新加坡零售網點 重心繼續向財富管理傾斜\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KrlBONKvp4llsGK5Vc138w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-03/ba215290-f64f-11ef-9ff3-04ecd0718408\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">滙豐縮減新加坡零售網點 重心繼續向財富管理傾斜</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
